snippet.title: Spice and Wolf: The Wind that Spans the Sea English Trailer
snippet.description:
A partially remastered version of the original trailer for the English patch. Press CC for subs!

Find out more, and grab the download here: https://agtteam.net/holo2

Fancy getting involved with our mission to bring out more awesome anime games in English? Join our Discord server at: https://discord.com/invite/UUF7Zbm
